  * Positioned before "View Code" button

Feature 2: Expanded Metrics (6 → 13 metrics)
- Added 7 new impact metric cards beyond original 6:
  1. **Idempotency Score** (+180%): Tracks safe re-run capability
  2. **Deployment Speed** (+400%): Measures time reduction (60min → 12min)
  3. **Testability & Coverage** (+350%): Zero tests → Molecule framework
  4. **Configuration Complexity** (-75%): Cyclomatic complexity reduction
  5. **Technical Debt** (-92%): Hours of cleanup work reduction
  6. **Audit & Compliance** (+500%): SOC 2, ISO 27001, PCI DSS readiness
- Added HTML cards for all 7 new metrics (lines 887-922)
- Created detailed modal content for each metric (lines 1474-1682):
  * Each modal explains: What it means, Why it matters, Contributing issues, Benefits
  * Idempotency: Explains safe re-runs, configuration drift, CI/CD readiness
  * Deployment Speed: 45-60min → 8-12min via async downloads & caching
  * Testability: Molecule framework integration, 80%+ coverage goal
  * Complexity: Cyclomatic complexity 127 → 32, refactoring benefits
  * Technical Debt: 120 hours → 10 hours of cleanup work
  * Audit Compliance: Passing SOC 2, ISO 27001, PCI DSS, HIPAA, FedRAMP
- Added calculation logic for all 7 new metrics (lines 1957-1985):
  * Idempotency: Issues #7, #24, #28, #39
  * Deployment Speed: Issues #34, #35, #39, #40
  * Testability: Issues #31-33, #59, #61, #66
  * Complexity: Issues #6, #8, #9, #10
  * Technical Debt: 21 issues across architecture, security, documentation
  * Audit Compliance: Issues #14, #17, #18, #56-58
- Updated recalculateAll() to update all 13 metric displays (lines 2036-2041)
- All metrics now update dynamically as issues are completed

Technical Implementation:
- Sub-item modal uses same overlay system as impact modal for consistency
- Modal content dynamically generated from subItemDetails object
- Metrics table uses thead/tbody structure for proper semantics
- CSS grid for responsive impact metrics layout
- Color-coded table cells (.metric-bad, .metric-good) for visual clarity
- Both "ℹ️ Details" button AND title click trigger modal
- event.stopPropagation() prevents checkbox toggle when clicking buttons

User Experience Improvements:
- Clicking sub-items now reveals extensive context and remediation steps
- Before/after metrics quantify impact of fixing each issue
- Step-by-step fix instructions reduce guesswork
- 13 comprehensive metrics provide full project health visibility
- All metrics clickable for detailed explanations
- Green "Details" buttons clearly distinguish from purple "Code" buttons
- Hover effects guide user interaction

