v0.1.4 | 2025-12-28 | Claude Code integration - Markdown export & issue prompts
================================================================================
Feature 1: Export to Markdown Checklist
- Added "📋 Export Markdown Checklist" button to header export section
- Generates comprehensive markdown file organized by phase
- Downloads as `ansible-issues-checklist.md`
- Markdown structure:
  * Project metadata (total/completed/remaining issues)
  * Issues grouped by Phase 1-7
  * Checkbox format: `- [ ]` for incomplete, `- [x]` for complete
  * Each issue includes: severity, priority, time estimate, description
  * Sub-items listed with file locations in backticks
  * Progress tracking per phase: "Phase 1 (3/10 completed)"
  * Backlog section for unphased issues
- Ideal for:
  * Planning Claude Code sessions
  * Tracking progress across sessions
  * Documentation and handoff
  * Sharing with team members

Feature 2: Copy Issue Prompt Button
- Added "Actions" column to issues table (9th column)
- Green "📋 Copy Prompt" button on every issue row
- Generates ready-to-paste Claude Code prompts
- Prompt includes:
  * Issue title, severity, priority, time, phase
  * Problem description
  * All files/locations to fix
  * Current code snippets (with syntax highlighting markers)
  * Step-by-step fix instructions (from subItemDetails)
  * Requirements checklist for Claude
- Button feedback: Changes to "✅ Copied!" for 2 seconds
- Clipboard integration via navigator.clipboard API
- Sub-items marked with ✅ (completed) or ⬜ (pending)

Implementation Details:
- Added exportToMarkdown() function (lines 2555-2614)
  * Iterates through issues by phase
  * Formats as GitHub-flavored markdown
  * Creates blob and triggers download
- Added copyIssuePrompt(issueId) function (lines 2616-2677)
  * Looks up issue from issues array
  * Pulls code snippets from codeSnippets object
  * Pulls fix instructions from subItemDetails object
  * Strips HTML tags from instructions with regex
  * Copies to clipboard with visual feedback
- Added .copy-prompt-btn CSS styling (lines 759-775)
  * Green gradient background (#10B981 → #059669)
  * Compact size (6px 12px padding, 0.75em font)
  * Hover effect with scale and shadow
  * white-space: nowrap prevents text wrapping
- Updated table colspan from 8 to 9 (line 2274)
- Added Actions column header (line 962)

Workflow Integration:
- **Before starting work**: Click "Export Markdown Checklist" to get overview
- **For each issue**: Click "Copy Prompt" → paste into Claude Code
- **After completion**: Check off issue in dashboard
- **Track progress**: Markdown export shows what's done vs remaining

User Experience:
- One-click access to formatted prompts for Claude
- No manual copying/pasting of issue details
- All context included: files, code, instructions
- Visual feedback when copied successfully
- Persistent progress tracking via localStorage
- Export for session planning and documentation

